folder: Olinville Avenue & Duncomb Avenue, Bronx, NY
text:
Olinville Ave., west side, adjoining and at its junction with Duncomb Ave. The first house is the home of the Goodfellows Club.
June 1, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

folder: Olinville Avenue & Duncomb Street, Bronx, NY
text:
Intersection of Olinville Avenue (left) and Duncomb Street,
looking south from the Bronx River Parkway.
May 12, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
